[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":83},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Farchives\u002Fpage\u002F88\u002F":3,"archive-page:zh-Hant:88":4,"author-stats:zh-Hant:full":81},null,{"posts":5,"total":79,"totalPages":80},[6,15,21,28,36,44,52,58,64,73],{"url":7,"title":8,"date":9,"updated":3,"category":10,"tags":11,"description":13,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190620\u002F3794703376\u002F","CoffeeScript 基礎學習","2019-06-20 10:52:16","JavaScript",[10,12],"CoffeeScript","由於可能專案使用上的需求將會撰寫 CoffeeScript，所以這邊就來稍微摸一下 CoffeeScript 是什麼鬼，又可以用什麼方式來撰寫","2",{"url":16,"title":17,"date":18,"updated":3,"category":10,"tags":19,"description":20,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190619\u002F3418592009\u002F","JavaScript 扁平化多維陣列","2019-06-19 14:45:37",[10],"今天遇到一個需求需要將多維陣列扁平化，這邊紀錄一下我查到的資料該怎麼做，順便記錄一下今天看到的 ES 2019 的方式",{"url":22,"title":23,"date":24,"updated":3,"category":10,"tags":25,"description":27,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190618\u002F3285272502\u002F","GitHub API contents file date 亂碼解決方法","2019-06-18 11:40:06",[10,26],"GitHub","這幾天在使用 GitHub API 中的一個 API 方法發現 content 會出現亂碼問題，這邊紀錄一下該如何解決 content 亂碼",{"url":29,"title":30,"date":31,"updated":3,"category":10,"tags":32,"description":35,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190617\u002F3829122039\u002F","使用 Google Apps Script 解決 CORS 問題","2019-06-17 13:24:47",[10,33,34],"Google Apps Script","CORS","前端打 API 遇到 CORS 又沒法改後端怎麼辦？這一篇從同源政策（Same-origin policy）的概念講起，用 Google Apps Script 包一層 Proxy 把第三方 API 變成你自己的同源 API， 繞過 CORS 限制。",{"url":37,"title":38,"date":39,"updated":3,"category":40,"tags":41,"description":42,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20190616\u002F2530364388\u002F","hexo-generator-search 搜尋套件 & 問題","2019-06-16 15:48:32","Hexo",[40],"基本上我們的 Hexo 主題都會使用到搜尋的套件，大多都會使用 hexo-generator-search 這邊紀錄一下一些優化的設置吧。","1",{"url":45,"title":46,"date":47,"updated":3,"category":48,"tags":49,"description":50,"readingMinutes":51},"\u002Fgit\u002F20190615\u002F4143994266\u002F","GitHub 該如何發 PR(pull request)","2019-06-15 21:33:52","Git",[26,48],"PR 是一個很特別的 GitHub 機制，當然 Gitlab 也有相同的機制，可是我這邊主要只會介紹使用 GitHub 如何發 PR 唷。","3",{"url":53,"title":54,"date":55,"updated":3,"category":48,"tags":56,"description":57,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fgit\u002F20190615\u002F1148594701\u002F","基礎 Git 指令","2019-06-15 13:59:25",[48],"這篇文章其實放在我的 EverNote 很久了，但是因為要整理一下 EverNote 特別拿出來重新寫一下作為一個紀錄，也是方便自己之後查找...",{"url":59,"title":60,"date":61,"updated":3,"category":48,"tags":62,"description":63,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fgit\u002F20190614\u002F391412804\u002F","fatal: unable to access XXx The requested URL returned error: 403","2019-06-14 21:38:14",[26,48],"今天在使用 Git Push 的時候發生一件很奇怪的事情，一直跳 remote Permission to xxx.git denied to user，這邊紀錄一下解決方法",{"url":65,"title":66,"date":67,"updated":3,"category":68,"tags":69,"description":72,"readingMinutes":43},"\u002Fother\u002F20190614\u002F1907905725\u002F","前端開發的 User Story","2019-06-14 21:07:23","雜談",[70,71],"User story","User stories","先前稍微瞭解過 User Story，但是這幾天實際 run 一次的時候卻發現一件很重要的事情，以往我在後端開發的時候都是以功能來考量...",{"url":74,"title":75,"date":76,"updated":3,"category":10,"tags":77,"description":78,"readingMinutes":14},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20190614\u002F4085828838\u002F","ES6 Template String 雙陣列處理方式","2019-06-14 20:11:14",[10],"今天在撰寫 JavaScript 的時候發生一件事情，就是在 ES6 中的 Template String 在處理一次陣列的方式，這邊做一下紀錄怎麼處理",1035,104,{"postCount":79,"tagCount":82},1009,1784013044160]